---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AztecPattern from '../../components/decorative/AztecPattern.astro';
import GeometricBorder from '../../components/decorative/GeometricBorder.astro';
import CircuitFeather from '../../components/CircuitFeather.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The World of Mirador"
  description="Explore the narrative world of Mirador and its attention-based economy."
>
  <!-- Hero Section with Pattern -->
  <div class="relative py-24 bg-primary-800">
    <AztecPattern pattern="codex" opacity={0.15} color="#A63D2F" className="hero-pattern" />
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
        <CircuitFeather severity="minor" size="lg" animated={true} />
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-white tracking-wider">The World of Mirador</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-200 max-w-2xl">
        A futuristic city-state where attention is currency, technology shapes reality,
        and competing powers struggle for control of capabilities.
      </p>
      <GeometricBorder type="horizontal" color="accent" className="mt-8 w-32" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="bg-primary-900 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-accent-400">The Attention Economy</h2>
        <GeometricBorder type="horizontal" color="accent" className="mb-6 w-24" />
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-neutral-200">
          In Mirador, attention is the most valuable resource. Citizens pay and earn through their focus
          and engagement, facilitated by advanced augmented reality systems that seamlessly overlay daily life.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-neutral-200">
          The Toltec Corporation, led by John Lawson, maintains the technological infrastructure that enables 
          this attention economy. Through specialized capabilities developed in their labs, Toltec creates 
          the systems that harvest, process, and monetize human focus.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-800 p-8 rounded-lg border border-primary-700 my-12 relative overflow-hidden">
          <AztecPattern pattern="flow" opacity={0.1} color="#A63D2F" className="quote-pattern" />
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <CircuitFeather severity="critical" size="md" className="mr-4" />
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-medium text-accent-400">From the Toltec Manifesto</h3>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-lg italic text-neutral-200 pl-6 border-l-4 border-accent-500">
              "Attention isn't just the new oil—it's the new oxygen. Those who control its flow control life itself. We've built a system where every glance has value, every moment of focus generates wealth, and no one need ever be bored again."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-right text-sm text-neutral-400 mt-4">— John Lawson, Toltec Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 mt-12 text-accent-400">The City-State Network</h2>
        <GeometricBorder type="horizontal" color="accent" className="mb-6 w-24" />
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-neutral-200">
          Mirador exists within a network of competing city-states, each established by different billionaire 
          visionaries with distinct approaches to organizing society. While Mirador controls the core 
          attention-processing capabilities, other enclaves have developed their own specialties.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Mirador</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-300">The central authority, focused on attention processing and capability development, ruled by the Toltec Corporation.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">New Valencia</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-300">A commercial hub with an entrepreneurial spirit, constantly pushing boundaries and testing the limits of their licensing agreements.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Arcadia</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-300">An arts-focused enclave that values creative expression above all else, often struggling with their capability compliance.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Nexus</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-300">A technology development center that creates innovative applications of Mirador's capabilities, sometimes with unexpected consequences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 mt-12 text-accent-400">The Capability System</h2>
        <GeometricBorder type="horizontal" color="accent" className="mb-6 w-24" />
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-neutral-200">
          Toltec licenses its attention-processing capabilities to other cities through formal agreements 
          that specify usage limits and compliance requirements. Each capability serves a specific function 
          in the attention economy:
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-8">
          <div class="flex">
            <CircuitFeather severity="minor" size="md" className="mr-4 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Vision</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-300">Analyzes and processes patterns of attention, identifying valuable trends and anomalies.</p>
              <a href="/technical/capabilities?mode=technical" class="text-secondary-400 hover:text-secondary-300 transition-colors text-sm mt-2 inline-block">Technical details →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex">
            <CircuitFeather severity="moderate" size="md" className="mr-4 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Learning</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-300">Shapes cognitive development and knowledge acquisition, forming the backbone of education systems.</p>
              <a href="/technical/capabilities?mode=technical" class="text-secondary-400 hover:text-secondary-300 transition-colors text-sm mt-2 inline-block">Technical details →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex">
            <CircuitFeather severity="severe" size="md" className="mr-4 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Spectacle</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-300">Creates immersive entertainment experiences that capture attention and generate significant revenue.</p>
              <a href="/technical/capabilities?mode=technical" class="text-secondary-400 hover:text-secondary-300 transition-colors text-sm mt-2 inline-block">Technical details →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex">
            <CircuitFeather severity="critical" size="md" className="mr-4 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-accent-400">Creation</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-300">Enables the development of new content and experiences, fundamental to cultural production.</p>
              <a href="/technical/capabilities?mode=technical" class="text-secondary-400 hover:text-secondary-300 transition-colors text-sm mt-2 inline-block">Technical details →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 mt-12 text-accent-400">The Manifestations</h2>
        <GeometricBorder type="horizontal" color="accent" className="mb-6 w-24" />
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-neutral-200">
          When capability usage exceeds licensed limits or falls out of balance, strange phenomena occur 
          throughout the city. These manifestations of system imbalance range from minor visual anomalies 
          to major social disruptions:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <CircuitFeather severity="minor" size="sm" className="mr-3" />
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-accent-400">Minor: Visual Anomalies</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 mt-2">
              Confetti transforms into feathers, holographic interfaces display unexpected patterns, and augmented reality overlays briefly glitch.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <CircuitFeather severity="moderate" size="sm" className="mr-3" />
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-accent-400">Moderate: System Instabilities</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 mt-2">
              Infrastructure services experience disruptions, communications become unreliable, and automated systems behave unpredictably.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <CircuitFeather severity="severe" size="sm" className="mr-3" />
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-accent-400">Severe: Economic Impacts</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 mt-2">
              Attention markets crash, automated financial systems fail, and currency values fluctuate wildly, causing widespread economic distress.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary-800 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <CircuitFeather severity="critical" size="sm" className="mr-3" />
              <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-accent-400">Critical: Social Unrest</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 mt-2">
              Civil disorder erupts, resistance movements gain traction, and the social fabric of the city begins to tear apart.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-700 p-8 rounded-lg mt-12 border border-primary-600 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
          <AztecPattern pattern="tribute" opacity={0.08} color="#FFC107" className="cta-pattern" />
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mb-4 text-white">Explore Silas's Journey</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-200 mb-6">
              Follow Silas Hale, a Nextla Agent responsible for monitoring capability compliance across the city-states, as he navigates the complex politics and moral dilemmas of the attention economy.
            </p>
            <a href="/narrative/silas?mode=narrative" class="inline-block bg-accent-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-accent-600 transition-colors shadow-md">
              Meet Silas Hale
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout> 